data.description: Well-maintained home in the heart of the Shenandoah Valley.  Only minutes to recreational areas like Bryce Resort and Lake Laura.  Visit wineries, hike the national forest, mountain bike, ski, or take advantage of the many other recreational opportunities in the area.  Home features a manicured 1.05+/- acre lot, full finished basement, spacious deck, and a large detached garage all set in a secluded location.  Other amenities include installed visible fence (White Flags Around Are Not Property Line) and a community pond for residents to enjoy.
